a podcast network

00:49:53.760 --> 00:49:56.070 align:middle line:90%
called the Be Here Now Network.

00:49:56.070 --> 00:49:58.750 align:middle line:84%
He invited me to start
hosting a podcast with them,

00:49:58.750 --> 00:50:00.570 align:middle line:84%
which, again, it
was like, really?

00:50:00.570 --> 00:50:02.430 align:middle line:90%
Twist my arm, you know?

00:50:02.430 --> 00:50:04.010 align:middle line:90%
>>LISA: You're really amazing.

00:50:04.010 --> 00:50:07.900 align:middle line:84%
I mean, you really have gotten
into some incredible places

00:50:07.900 --> 00:50:08.700 align:middle line:90%
in your life.

